## ğŸ§  What This Teaches

* Prompts are **evidence of process**
* AI use requires **discernment and editing**
* Revision is not just about textâ€”itâ€™s about *questions asked*

Students learn that writing with AI is not shortcuttingâ€”itâ€™s shaping. Prompts are the intellectual fingerprints of their work.

