## ğŸ” Instructor Checkpoints

Use the following when reviewing prompt logs:

| Signal                        | What It Shows                                      |
| ----------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------- |
| Multiple attempts             | Student is iterating, not offloading               |
| Specific prompts              | Student understands the tool, not just the topic   |
| â€œWhyâ€ reflection              | Student is noticing bias, vagueness, or overreach  |
| Self-generated â€œshould-havesâ€ | Student is building discernment, not faking output |

